This course has been tested with the following software versions:

npm 8.15
node 16.17.0
tsc 4.7.4
React 18.2.0
Spring Boot 2.7.3

https://github.com/selvaswe/fullstack-react-and-springboot/blob/main/install-react-tools/ms-windows/install-ms-windows.md

> node --version
> npm --version

> npm install --location=global typescript@4.7.4

>tsc --version

Creat New React application 
>npx create-react-app myapp
>cd myapp
>npm start
 the aobe command will 
  1 build the app (comple/transpile)
  2 Start the server
  3 Watch the source files
  4 Rebuild the app when soucre is updated (hot reload)

> set PORT=5100 && npm start 
